WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 493
Chapter 493
(Senate Bill 418)
AN ACT concerning
Professional Licensing Portability – Members of the Foreign Service and
Spouses
FOR the purpose of authorizing members of the Foreign Service and spouses of members
of the Foreign Service, under certain circumstances, to practice in the State under
an occupational or professional license issued in another jurisdiction; and generally
relating to occupational and professional licensing of members of the Foreign Service
and their spouses.
