Article – Business Occupations and Professions
1–101.
(a) In this article the following words have the meanings indicated.
(e) “Department” means the Maryland Department of Labor.
2–101.
(a) In this title the following words have the meanings indicated.
(d) “Board” means the State Board of Public Accountancy.
2–301.
Except as provided in § 2–321 of this subtitle OR § 10–14A–03 OF THE STATE
GOVERNMENT ARTICLE, an individual shall be licensed by the Board before the
